    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Unifies 267 scattered DOT Open Data assets around the LION street segment behind one agent contract, and adds the net-new street-work permit application.",
